<p>Unless otherwise permitted by the prior written approval of the Commission or a person authorized by the Commission, the licensee shall, in respect of a radioactive nuclear substance set out in the Appendix: Nuclear Substances and Radiation Devices, or in the Appendix: Nuclear Substances and Class II Prescribed Equipment of this licence, report in writing to the Commission or a person authorized by the Commission any transfer, receipt, import or export of any sealed source:</p>
